'''War Office form 22 November 1916''' is a form from the service record of the [[Wikipedia:War Office|War Office]], in which [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] confirms his return to England from France due to trench fever (dated [[22 November]] [[1916]]).<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=http://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/pathways/firstworldwar/people/p_tolkien_med.htm|articlename=J R R Tolkien: trench fever|dated=|website=[http://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk NationalArchives.co.uk]|accessed=29 July 2012}}</ref>
